{"tid":1450803,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"「警察還眼」明天1PM全民入機場 百萬人塞爆機場","createTime":"2019-08-11T17:57:48.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-11T19:11:48.000Z","uid":154017,"like":20,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"59b5a042a85674ed6a47e677634e70b21981212d","tid":1450803,"uid":154017,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T17:57:48.000Z","msg":"一人一Post狂洗連登 ［所有台］<br />\n唔該你出一份力，肯出post，聽日就係人都知入機場<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n標題：「警察還眼」明天1PM全民入機場 百萬人塞爆機場<br />\n<br />\n無時間文宣<br />\n見POST者，自行Copy開新Post，要連登全部都係呢個Post<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n812起 1PM，有人性既你立刻罷工，百萬人進入機場，咩都唔做，勢要討回雙眼<br />\n機場因為100萬人係機場而暫停運作，不是們的責任，是因為機場不夠大<br />\n圍到出青馬，都全條橋唔夠闊<br />\n<br />\n統一口號，兩句，要入健力士，等歷史知道<br />\n「黑警還眼」<br />\n「五大訴求，缺一不可」<br />\n<br />\n黑警聽住：<br />\n一係你就入機場殺哂所有人<br />\n一係你就還返隻眼出黎<br />\n否則百萬人不離開機場<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n大群：<a href=\"https://t.me/airport730\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fairport730&d=bqZDxu8XrC4QaJB2Smgqvnfp3ZHOIdf2SFoQnphXrww%3D&h=a21d4ecc\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/airport730</a><br />\n實時Channel: <a href=\"https://t.me/hk730air\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fhk730air&d=bqZDxu8XrC4QaJB2Smgqvnfp3ZHOIdf2SFoQnphXrww%3D&h=7926a381\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/hk730air</a>"},{"pid":"3b612190656f1e1d3c5fb2a696ece97da6e5f093","tid":1450803,"uid":154017,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T17:58:10.000Z","msg":"一齊文宣開Lo"},{"pid":"ff33660932ab063b3a48e213e1c8edb2d01336bd","tid":1450803,"uid":154017,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T17:58:26.000Z","msg":"聽日我要見到你地！"},{"pid":"02c6eaf0560d308247abc40f81f9b4a9fb3a72d5","tid":1450803,"uid":283109,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T17:58:35.000Z","msg":"機場文宣整合post<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1450351\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1450351</a><br />\n<br />\n「警察還眼」明天1PM全民入機場 百萬人塞爆機場"},{"pid":"6